Draw, either event/quest/tournament
  quest
    player chooses to sponsor or not, possibly no sponsors
    players choose to participate or not
    use weapons/foes/armours/allies/tests
    players drop out, players complete
  event
    event involving current player, all players, some players
  tournament
    players draw either foe/ally/weapon/armour
    players play variable amount of and possibly differing cards (of note 0 cards, or identical cards)
    compare battle points/handle ties
move to next turn.
